Plugin: backtrace
Summary: enable display of backtraces on scheme errors
Release: 1.0
TeXmacs: 1.0.2
Author: David Allouche
License: Public domain

TeXmacs supports GUILE facilities for displaying backtraces when an exception
is not handled. However this feature is not enable by default.

This plugin enable the scheme backtrace facility and will cause texmacs to
provide helpful debugging information when an error occurs in scheme code.
